</title>
<subSubSection id="1F0C0E77E4B4FE10633C2EFFCFDF3EED" pageId="null" pageNumber="490" type="description">
<paragraph id="A55ABC5CFFF28C279EF2C33FD42FB03F" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="10CB1C9A71FC4373B83420C9257C72FC" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Aronicum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="490" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="clusii">
<emphasis id="E7AA94344AD366BA994006F7D1F0BD72" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">D. Clusii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 5) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="EE3E8C8E7BD7A72E47A744C3C7CB6DAB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">
Stengel nicht hohl; am Blattrand oft mehrzellige 
<normalizedToken id="3A7C4DAABE4EC83F4FA3E62D0835BBE5" originalValue="Drüsenhaare" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">Druesenhaare</normalizedToken>
, dagegen sind die sehr 
<normalizedToken id="AD797345070554F5D7DECE37821896DB" originalValue="dünnen" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">duennen</normalizedToken>
, krausen Haare nie vorhanden.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="B5DC71D7573D2B8509765E8AEEE3C7B9" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B99C9A85C861C80F67512BF0AC3E23D3" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">
<emphasis id="28D00F6D253CA3B046FBA5381725025B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="066C23EC40B2B170DCA8003C5DE7E4C2" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">
<emphasis id="A710B6C87F25FEA33316B70E17F8C083" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">Standort.</emphasis>
Alpin, seltener subalpin. Steinige, lange vom Schnee bedeckte, kalkhaltige und kalkarme 
<normalizedToken id="81682E50B516C0C7F76A5D9133A4A174" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Schutthalden, 
<normalizedToken id="2EACE0E792A4A6FB383A9DF2F3056BEF" originalValue="Moränen" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">Moraenen</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2545DE8B50FC1997166BB8DBC2D15E59" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">
<emphasis id="4AAA42473BDC2E85ED8EFC4DAED891EA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">Verbreitung. Ostalpen-Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="34EC6CA9FEB57D54A8E44267195622C1" originalValue="Westwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">Westwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis ins mittlere Tirol und in die Bergamasker Alpen. - Im Gebiet: Bergamasker Alpen (Monte Biandino, Pizzo Arera, Presolana, Val Camonica, Monte Pisgana, Monte Frerone, Monte Avaro), Adamello- und Ortlergebirge (vom Stilfser Joch 
<normalizedToken id="D79BCAA3521FAA3CD13FAFAE2365D78E" originalValue="südostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="490">suedostwaerts</normalizedToken>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
